  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and saute until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and saute for another minute.",
    "Add the birds eye chillies and saute for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder and saute for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coconut milk, tomato puree, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or with some crusty bread."
